					<div class="chapter">Chapter 13</div>
					|<div class="next-chapter"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210918095155/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Est/ch_14">next &gt;</a></div>
				</div>
				<div class="chapters">
					<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210918095155/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Est/ch_1">1</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210918095155/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Est/ch_2">2</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210918095155/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Est/ch_3">3</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210918095155/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Est/ch_4">4</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210918095155/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Est/ch_5">5</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210918095155/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Est/ch_6">6</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210918095155/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Est/ch_7">7</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210918095155/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Est/ch_8">8</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210918095155/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Est/ch_9">9</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210918095155/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Est/ch_10">10</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210918095155/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Est/ch_11">11</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210918095155/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Est/ch_12">12</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210918095155/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Est/ch_13" class="active">13</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210918095155/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Est/ch_14">14</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210918095155/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Est/ch_15">15</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210918095155/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Est/ch_16">16</a> 				</div>
